\c 5
\s Ukungagcwalisi izifungo kuyibuthutha
\p
\v 1 Gcina unyawo lwakho\x + 5.7. Eks. 3.5. 30.18-20. Isa. 1.12.\x* nxa usiya endlini kaNkulunkulu\x + Gen. 28.17.\x*; sondelela ukulalela kulokunikela umhlatshelo wezithutha, ngoba kazazi ukuthi zenza okubi\x + 1 Sam. 15.22. Zaga 15.8.\x*.
\v 2 Ungabi lamawala ngomlomo wakho, lenhliziyo yakho ingaphangisi ukukhupha ilizwi phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + 7.9.\x*; ngoba uNkulunkulu usemazulwini, wena-ke usemhlabeni, ngakho amazwi akho kawabe malutshwana\x + Mat. 6.7.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba iphupho liza ngobunengi bomsebenzi\x + 8.16. 1.13.\x*, lelizwi lesithutha ngobunengi bamazwi\x + Jobe 11.2. Zaga 10.19.\x*.
\v 4 Lapho ufunga isifungo kuNkulunkulu\x + Nani 30.2.\x*, ungaphuzi ukusikhokha\x + Hlab. 50.14. Zaga 20.23.\x*, ngoba kakulantokozo kuziwula; khokha lokho okufungileyo\x + 3.1.\x*.
\v 5 Kungcono ukuthi ungafungi kulokuthi ufunge ungakhokhi.
\v 6 Ungavumeli umlomo wakho ukuthi wenze inyama yakho yone\x + Gen. 3.10-12.\x*, futhi ungatsho phambi kwengilosi\x + 8.5. 1 Kor. 11.10. Mal. 2.7. Eks. 14.19. Nani 15.25,26.\x* ukuthi bekuyisiphosiso; uNkulunkulu uzathukuthelelani ilizwi lakho, achithe umsebenzi wezandla zakho\x + 5.1. Levi 4.2.\x*?
\v 7 Ngoba ebunengini bamaphupho lamazwi kukhona lokuyize okunengi, kodwa mesabe uNkulunkulu\x + 12.13.\x*.
\s Konke kuyize
\p
\v 8 Uba ubona\x + 3.16. 4.1.\x* ucindezelo lomyanga\x + Hez. 18.18.\x* lokuphanjulwa kokulunga lesahlulelo ngodlakela\x + Hez. 18.18.\x* esabelweni\x + 2.8.\x*, ungamangali ngalinto, ngoba ophezulu kophezulu uyananzelela, njalo kulabaphezulu phezu kwabo\x + Hlab. 12.5.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Lenzuzo yomhlabathi ngeyabo bonke; inkosi isetshenzelwa yinsimu\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 10 Othanda imali kayikweneliswa yimali, njalo othanda okunengi kayi\add kweneliswa\add* yikwanda; lokhu lakho kuyize\x + Hlab. 37.16.\x*.
\v 11 Ekwandeni kokuhle, bayanda abakudlayo; njalo kulenzuzo bani\x + 2.21.\x* kubanini bakho, ngaphandle koku\add ku\add*buka ngamehlo abo\x + 5.13. 7.12. 8.8. Zaga 3.27.\x*?
\v 12 Bumnandi ubuthongo besisebenzi loba sisidla okulutshwana loba okunengi; kodwa ukusutha kwesinothi kakusivumeli ukulala.
\v 13 Kukhona\x + 6.1.\x* ububi obubuhlungu \add e\add*sengibubonile ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 5.16.\x*: Inotho egcinelwe abaniniyo kube yibubi kibo\x + 5.13. 7.12. 8.8. Zaga 3.27.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa leyonotho ichitheka ngomsebenzi omubi\x + 1.13.\x*: Esezala umntwana, kungaselalutho esandleni sakhe.
\v 15 Njengokuphuma kwakhe esiswini sikanina, uzabuyela eze ehamba njengokuza kwakhe; njalo kayikuthatha lutho lomtshikatshika wakhe angahamba lalo esandleni sakhe\x + Jobe 1.21. Hlab. 49.17.\x*.
\v 16 Lokhu lakho kuyibubi obubuhlungu\x + 5.16.\x*, kukho konke njengokufika kwakhe ngokunjalo uzahamba. Njalo ulenzuzo bani\x + 1.3.\x* owatshikatshikela umoya\x + Zaga 11.29.\x*?
\v 17 Njalo insuku zakhe zonke udlela emnyameni, \add e\add*losizi olukhulu, lomkhuhlane wakhe, lokuthukuthela\x + Hlab. 127.2.\x*?
\p
\v 18 Khangela, engikubonileyo mina, kulungile okuhle ukudla lokunatha\x + 2.24.\x* lokubona okuhle emtshikatshikeni wakhe wonke awutshikatshikayo ngaphansi kwelanga, \add e\add*nani\add ni\add* lensuku zempilo yakhe uNkulunkulu amnike zona\x + 2.1.\x*, ngoba kuyisabelo sakhe\x + 2.10.\x*.
\v 19 Laye wonke umuntu, uNkulunkulu amnike inotho\x + 6.2. Jobe 1.21.\x* lengcebo\x + 2 Lan. 1.11.\x*, wamnika amandla okudla kukho, lokuthatha isabelo sakhe, lokuthokoza emtshikatshikeni wakhe - lokhu kuyisipho sikaNkulunkulu\x + 3.13.\x*.
\v 20 Ngoba kayikukhumbula kakhulu insuku zempilo yakhe, ngoba uNkulunkulu u\add m\add*phendula ngentokozo yenhliziyo yakhe.
